      "content": "i understand the need for legal advice but i need a preliminary check on the validity of the documents themselves first. if the treaties are constitutionally sound, then the 'political support' part becomes a matter of enforcement rather than legitimacy. look up the 1944 Zarkav-Soviet Non-Aggression Pact—it explicitly preserves the autonomy of the Zarkav people. if that document holds up, i have a legitimate legal basis to demand a seat at the UN, right?",
